How to resist camp approval quickly?

To get your ad approved quickly, make sure to follow NewsBreak's policies and guidelines closely when creating your ad. The approval process usually takes between 1-2 business days. You can find more details on how to create your first ad here: [How to create your first ad](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/17618196971149-How-to-create-your-first-ad).
I have posted an ad but it is not approved?

I'm sorry to hear that your ad hasn't been approved yet. The approval process usually takes between 1-2 business days. If your ad was rejected, you can check the reasons for rejection and make necessary adjustments. For more details on what to do next, please refer to this article: [My ad got rejected - What's next](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/18085960681101-My-ad-got-rejected-What-s-next).

Our support team is available to assist you during regular business hours. If you have any specific questions or need assistance, feel free to reach out, and we'll get back to you as soon as possible.
I need to contact support privately, where should I send it?
You can contact our support team by emailing adsupport@newsbreak.com. Please provide as much detail as possible about your issue so we can assist you more effectively.
